---
// FAQ and CTA merged section with teal wave
---

<section class="faq-cta-wrapper">
  <!-- Teal wave background -->
  <div class="wave-background">
    <svg class="wave wave-1" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path fill="rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.3)" d="M0,192L48,197.3C96,203,192,213,288,229.3C384,245,480,267,576,250.7C672,235,768,181,864,181.3C960,181,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,181,1392,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
    </svg>
    <svg class="wave wave-2" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path fill="rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.2)" d="M0,64L48,80C96,96,192,128,288,128C384,128,480,96,576,90.7C672,85,768,107,864,144C960,181,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,181,1392,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Content -->
  <div class="faq-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-header animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="section-badge section-badge-dark">
          <span class="badge-dot"></span>
          FAQ
        </span>
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-light">
          Frequently Asked
          <span class="highlight-box">Questions</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

    <div class="faq-list">

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <span>What is Claude Code and how can it help my team?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Claude Code is a command-line tool from Anthropic that enables agentic coding with Claude. We help teams set up custom configurations, develop plugins, and train developers to maximize productivity with AI-assisted development workflows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <span>How long does a typical implementation take?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Implementation timelines vary based on scope. Starter setups can be completed in 1-2 weeks, while enterprise-wide deployments typically take 4-12 weeks. We'll provide a detailed timeline after our discovery call.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <span>Do you offer ongoing support after setup?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes! All tiers include support periods ranging from setup documentation to 90-day support with regular check-ins. Enterprise clients receive ongoing retainer relationships with priority support and quarterly workshops.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <span>What's included in each pricing tier?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Each tier builds on the previous: Starter includes basic setup and training, Growth adds custom plugins and extended support, Scale provides full architecture and team-wide training, and Enterprise offers unlimited customization with dedicated partnership.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          <span>Can you work with our existing tech stack?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Absolutely! We specialize in integrating with existing systems. Our solutions work with popular stacks including Google Cloud, n8n, Netlify, and various databases. We'll assess your current setup and design integrations accordingly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Content -->
  <div class="cta-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-light">
        Ready to Build Your <span class="highlight-box">AI System</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle section-subtitle-light">
        Let's discuss your project and create a custom solution that fits your needs. We typically respond within 24 hours.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="mailto:jeremy@intentsolutions.io" class="btn-primary">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>Get in Touch</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="btn-secondary-light">
          View Full Pricing
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-signals">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>No commitment required</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>24-hour response time</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>Free consultation call</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Merged FAQ + CTA Section */
  .faq-cta-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Teal wave background */
  .wave-background {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 60%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .wave-1 {
    animation: wave-float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .wave-2 {
    animation: wave-float 15s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  @keyframes wave-float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateX(0) translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateX(-20px) translateY(10px);
    }
  }

  /* FAQ Content */
  .faq-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-badge-dark {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-accent-secondary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: scale(1);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.2);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .section-title-light {
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle-light {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .highlight-box {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-highlight);
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin: 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .faq-question {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-light);
    transition: var(--transition-base);
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-secondary);
  }

  .faq-question span {
    flex: 1;
    padding-right: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .faq-item.active .faq-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
    max-height: 500px;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    color: var(--text-light-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* CTA Content */
  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 3rem 0 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    background: var(--text-light);
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 1.125rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: var(--transition-base);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .btn-secondary-light {
    background: var(--color-accent-primary);
    color: var(--text-light);
    padding: 1.125rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: var(--transition-base);
  }

  .btn-secondary-light:hover {
    background: #4f46e5;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .trust-signals {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .trust-item svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-content {
      padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
    }

    .cta-content {
      padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .faq-question {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 1.25rem 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary-light {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .trust-signals {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');

    faqItems.forEach(item => {
      const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');

      question?.addEventListener('click', () => {
        // Close other items (only one open at a time)
        faqItems.forEach(otherItem => {
          if (otherItem !== item) {
            otherItem.classList.remove('active');
          }
        });

        // Toggle current item
        item.classList.toggle('active');
      });
    });
  });
</script>
